---
description: Expo Router rules for route files
globs:
  - "app/**/*.ts"
  - "app/**/*.tsx"
alwaysApply: false
---

Rules for Expo route files:
- Route files should stay thin
- Avoid API logic inside route files
- Avoid large inline components
- Import hooks and business logic from src/features
- Keep screen-level composition here, not domain logic
- Prefer Expo Router conventions over custom routing abstractions
